column2: A belief system centered around worship of The Devil and his servants that are also seen as deities, Their origins can be traced in Russian folklore, history, literature and legends. Those parts of ancient and often distorted lore formed the new core of this faith.

A belief system centered around worship of The Devil and his servants that are also seen as deities, Their origins can be traced in Russian folklore, history, literature and legends. Those parts of ancient and often distorted lore formed the new core of this faith. Folklorist faith has now been codified in order to withstand attacks from neighboring religions.
